{"tid":1367823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察一人一證反黑心警","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:05:55.000Z","uid":124894,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30a37b090e7191f359ed435de8013bafb22e3beb","tid":1367823,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"「本人，謹以至誠作出宣言，本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令。</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n各位良心警察，你哋仲記得宣誓嘅內容嗎？而家內部有同事公然反對政務司司長，你哋仲可以容忍嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6fVFBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6fVFBj.jpg&h=7291a9b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82fea128a9953c678bb260101d5ae34e36259b1d","tid":1367823,"uid":124894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZLbdXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZLbdXi.png&h=0bc6f8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有更高級的<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">良心警</span></span>反對<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑心警</span></span>嗎？"},{"pid":"7807e25b3d0246687039c0b630efc3537c741d6b","tid":1367823,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"兩個兩粒勁過一個三粒<br />\n<br />\n兩個三粒勁過一個警司<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">良心警，你們在那裡?</span></span>"},{"pid":"f853a07b362cff7b1b095b04d4512ca454aba862","tid":1367823,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"警務人員在任何時間均須向政務司司長敬禮<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dqApKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dqApKT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2cc89489f815b82a658f5141f4c8d59d821cc90","tid":1367823,"uid":30743,